The longer it goes on and we don't get a grip and go back to work, the more businesses that will go out of business with people losing jobs.  Read up on the depression in the 30's and see if you want to go through that again, only 12 times worse.  Our future is not good because of this panic and ridiculous isolation of healthy people.
